dark-colored urine;
light-colored bowel movements;
difficulty breathing;
stomach pain
or swelling; nausea;
vomiting;
unusual muscle pain;
loss of appetite for at least a few days;
lack of energy;
flu-like symptoms; itching; feeling cold, especially in the arms or legs;
dizziness or lightheadedness;
fast or irregular heartbeat;
or extreme weakness or tiredness.
Keep all appointments with your doctor and the laboratory before, during, and for a few months after your treatment with adefovir.
